title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1995-03-17
description:
Set 1

Here Comes Sunshine, Wang Dang Doodle, Peggy-O, Queen Jane Approximately, Lazy River Road, Eternity*, Loose Lucy (55 mins)

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samba In The Rain-> Truckin'-> New Speedway Boogie-> Jam-> Drums-> Space-> All Along The Watchtower-> Standing On the Moon-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Lucy In The Sky With Diamonds (85 mins)

* Weir on acoustic; Several takes of Unbroken Chain were done for soundcheck/rehearsal.
